{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unserious Sandbox is exactly what its name suggests: an unserious sandbox, a playground free of rigid forms, where play itself is the only rule.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by Parkour and Counter-Strike\u2019s Surfing and KZ community, Unserious Sandbox revolves around the fun in movement. The gameplay focuses on freeform play, whether it is to traverse dynamic environments, toy with ragdoll physics, or simply idle. For those who do enjoy traversing dynamic environments, the game is\u00a0built inside Unreal Engine 5, utilizing motion-matching animation technology to deliver smooth yet responsive character control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are some traversal challenges, but no serious objectives\u2014just a space to experiment, move, and play at your own pace. <i>You bring it to life.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Flows &amp; Rhythms</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/TraverseUtopia.jpg?t=1740434151\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Ragdoll, whenever, wherever...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/Sandbox.TraversalGym.Ragdoll.png?t=1740434151\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Please note:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's UI features English with Chinese subtitles. This is intentional to add a layer of wordplay through the nuances of languages. Currently, the game is focusing on single-player experiences and does not plan to support multiplayer gameplay.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3391340?t=1740434151","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3391340?t=1740434151","ca